        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-400 p-6 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-600 mb-3">04</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Outdated Site = "Stagnant Agency"</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Forge's 3-year-old site: "Are you guys still in business?" prospects asked. Competitors launching fresh work weekly. Perception: Stagnant agency = declining quality = risky to hire. New site: Recent work, testimonials, current team. Perception: Active agency = growing quality = confident to hire. Inquiries 175% increase. Agency site freshness = capability perception.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-slate-500 p-6 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-700 mb-3">05</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">No Results Metrics = No Credibility</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Forge's portfolio: Pretty project images, no outcomes. Prospects: "Nice work, but did it perform?" New portfolio: Every project with metrics ("+340% leads," "18% conversion," "$2.3M revenue generated"). Results visible = capability proven = confidence to hire. Closed $45K branding retainer (client: "Your case studies show you deliver results, not just pretty designs"). Metrics matter.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-500 p-6 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-700 mb-3">06</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">No Testimonials = Trust Gap</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Forge's old site: Zero testimonials. "Why no client quotes?" prospects asked. New site: 3 video testimonials (30-second clips, real clients). Result? 43% more inquiries (social proof loop). Video testimonials 2.3x more effective than text (see client, hear emotion, trust immediately). Client vouching = your claims validated. Testimonials = shortest path to trust.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">UNEXPECTED FINDINGS</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-gray-50 border-[3px] border-slate-300 p-6">
          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-500 mb-3">175%</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Inquiry Increase With Fresh Site</h3>
