          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Qualified Leads With Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Services pricing visible. Qualified leads: 3 ‚Üí 12/month (300% increase). Serious clients see budget fits, inquire confidently.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-gray-50 border-[3px] border-slate-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-600 mb-3">$300K</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Revenue Lost Waiting For Perfect</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Forge: 18 months "in progress" = $300K lost leads ($50K/month √ó 6 months). Perfect never launched. Framer launched in 1 day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-slate-50 border-[3px] border-gray-400 p-6">
          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-gray-600 mb-3">73%</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Fewer Unqualified Inquiries</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Pricing visible = self-selection. Unqualified inquiries decreased 73%. Saves time = qualified only.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-gray-50 border-[3px] border-slate-500 p-6">
          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-700 mb-3">2.3x</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Video vs. Text Testimonials</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Video testimonials drive 2.3x more inquiries than text. See client, hear emotion, trust immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-slate-50 border-[3px] border-gray-500 p-6">
          <p class="text-6xl font-black text-gray-700 mb-3">1 Day</p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Framer Build vs. 18 Months Custom</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Forge: Custom build 18 months (never launched). Framer: 1 day build, launched immediately. Speed = revenue.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">AGENCY TOOL COMPARISONS</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-slate-300 p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class={`text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wider ${tool.name === 'Framer AI' ? 'bg-slate-500 text-white' : tool.name === '10Web AI' ? 'bg-gray-500 text-white' : 'bg-slate-600 text-white'} px-3 py-1 rounded-full`}>{tool.badge}</span>
              <span class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-500">{tool.rating}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">{tool.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-sm">{tool.verdict}</p>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <p class="font-black text-green-700 text-sm mb-2">PROS</p>
              <ul class="text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                {tool.pros.map(pro => <li>‚úì {pro}</li>)}
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <p class="font-black text-red-700 text-sm mb-2">CONS</p>
              <ul class="text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                {tool.cons.map(con => <li>‚úó {con}</li>)}
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="block w-full text-center bg-slate-500 text-white font-black py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">{tool.cta}</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Framer Deep Dive -->
      <div class="mb-12 bg-white border-[3px] border-slate-500 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-500">9.2</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">Framer AI</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Best for Design</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6">Exceptional design quality with fast builds and client handoff that impresses.</p>
        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-slate-400 pl-6 py-5 bg-slate-50 rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="font-black text-slate-800 mb-3">FORGE DIGITAL CASE STUDY: 175% INQUIRY INCREASE</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">18 months custom build paralysis. Agency site outdated, losing $50K/month leads. Framer: 1-day build, launched immediately. Portfolio reorganized (12 projects with results: "+340% leads"), services transparent (Branding $30-50K, Web $20-40K), team bios added, testimonials with results. Month 1: Inquiries 175% increase (8 ‚Üí 22), qualified leads 300% increase (3 ‚Üí 12). Month 3: Closed 4 retainers totaling $123K first-month revenue ($45K branding largest in agency history). Staff morale: "Finally proud to share our URL." Build cost: $1,200 (Framer $300 annual + freelancer $400 + 12 hours). ROI: $300K lost revenue recovered in 3 months. Key insight: Framer speed = ship fast = revenue start. Custom perfect = never launches = revenue zero. Framer wins for agencies where design quality = primary differentiator, portfolios and marketing sites, clients who care about modern aesthetics. But vendor lock-in: clients stuck in Framer ecosystem unless export purchased. White label not available (clients see Framer branding unless $25/month tier).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-black text-green-700 text-sm mb-2">WHY CHOOSE FRAMER</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
