        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-gray-400 pl-6 py-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">WORDPRESS AGENCY CASE STUDY: CLIENT HANDOFF FREEDOM</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">PixelPerfect Agency, WordPress-focused shop (80% of clients demand WP). Problem: Framer builds beautiful but locks clients into ecosystem. "Client wants WordPress, Framer doesn't export without payment. We're stuck supporting forever." Switched to 10Web: Generates WordPress sites (full export, WooCommerce included, plugin ecosystem). Client handoff: Client hires any WordPress developer, site supported. Agency free from endless support. Results: Client satisfaction increased 67% ("we can edit ourselves, not tied to agency"), agency time freed 12 hours/month (no more WordPress support tickets), new client inquiries increased 43% (WordPress shops prefer WP-native agencies). Revenue: Flat $220K/month ‚Üí $248K/month in 3 months (13% growth). 10Web wins for WordPress-heavy agencies: Export full WP site (client freedom), WooCommerce included (e-commerce clients), plugin ecosystem (any WP dev helps). But slower than Framer (generation 30-60 sec vs 2-5 min), requires WP knowledge (clients need hosting, plugins, updates), PageSpeed 75-85 (slower than Framer 95+).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-black text-green-700 text-sm mb-2">WHY CHOOSE 10WEB</p>
